'''Cloud computing''' allows users to use remote servers for both storage and [[computers |computing]] power. 

This requires massive [[data centers]] using very large amounts of [[energy]]. On the other hand, the proportion of [[embedded energy]] to energy usage is much lower than personal computers. 


